analysisPopulations.name: Screened set
analysisPopulations.text: The Screened set (SCR) includes all subjects who signed an informed consent form.
analysisPopulations.label: SCR
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Screened set (SCR) includes all subjects who signed an informed consent form.

analysisPopulations.name: Randomized set
analysisPopulations.text: The Randomized set (RS) includes all subjects who were randomized to a treatment group in the trial.
analysisPopulations.label: RS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Randomized set (RS) includes all subjects who were randomized to a treatment group in the trial.

analysisPopulations.name: Treated set
analysisPopulations.text: The Treated set (TS) includes all subjects who were randomized and received at least one dose of study drug.
analysisPopulations.label: TS
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Treated set (TS) includes all subjects who were randomized and received at least one dose of study drug.
analysisPopulations.criteria: Randomized AND received >=1 dose of study drug

analysisPopulations.name: Intention-to-treat set
analysisPopulations.text: The efficacy analyses will follow the intention-to-treat (ITT) principle in assigning patients to treatment groups, i.e. patients will be analysed as randomised. In this trial, the ITT approach is defined as the analysis of all randomized patients.
analysisPopulations.label: ITT
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The efficacy analyses will follow the intention-to-treat (ITT) principle in assigning patients to treatment groups, i.e. patients will be analysed as randomised. In this trial, the ITT approach is defined as the analysis of all randomized patients.

analysisPopulations.name: Treated set – Follow-up
analysisPopulations.text: The Treated set – Follow-up (TS-FU) includes all subjects in the Treated set who have completed the follow-up visit.
analysisPopulations.label: TS-FU
analysisPopulations.populationDescription: The Treated set – Follow-up (TS-FU) includes all subjects in the Treated set who have completed the follow-up visit.
analysisPopulations.criteria: In Treated set AND completed follow-up visit
